title: European Tango Championship 2019 – Tango de pista – Qualification Day 2 Ronda 1

creator: Lucio Demare & Raúl Berón
description:
Watch Ronda 1 from Qualification Day 2 during the European Tango Championship 2019 in Bellaria, Italy.

The dancers are (couples with a * moved to the Semi-Final)
*201 Chiara Luisi and Stefano Arioli – Italy
204 Xia Li and Denis Ballarin – Italy
205 Bernadette Moricard and Michel Marand – France
*207 Elena Shtitskaia and Dmitrii Muksinov – Russia
208 Ana Carolina Alberto Acosta and Brian Alexis Ceballos – Spain
*209 Alessia Romanazzi and Cristian Di Barbora – Italy
*210 Zaneta Leonidi and Takehiro Uto – Greece

The music was
Lucio Demare/Raúl Berón “Canta, pajarito”
Rodolfo Biagi/Hugo Duval “Triste comedia”
Ricardo Tanturi “Argañaraz”
